@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Quản trị viên" as User #Yellow
boundary "CustomerEditForm" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "JwtMiddleware" as MW #Yellow
control "CustomersController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "CustomerService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Customer" as CEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Mở form chỉnh sửa khách hàng
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Tải dữ liệu hiện tại\n(GET /api/Customers/{id} -> điền form)
UI -> UI : 1.2: Sửa thông tin\n(FullName, Email, Phone, Address,\nDateOfBirth, Gender, Nationality,\nPassportNumber, IdCard, IsActive)
UI -> API : 1.3: PUT /api/Customers/{id}\nHeader: Authorization: Bearer {token}\nBody: UpdateCustomerRequest
activate API

API -> API : 1.4: Axios interceptor: gắn Bearer token
API -> MW : 1.5: Request qua JwtMiddleware
activate MW
MW -> MW : 1.6: ValidateToken
alt 1.7: [Token không hợp lệ]
MW --> API : 1.7.1: 401
API --> UI : 1.7.2: Redirect login
else 1.8: [Token hợp lệ]
MW --> Ctrl : 1.8.1: Chuyển tiếp
deactivate MW

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.9: UpdateAsync(id, request)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.10: Customers.GetByIdAsync(id)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.10.1: Customer hoặc null
deactivate DB

alt 1.11: [Customer không tồn tại]
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.11.1: ApiResponse.Fail(\n"Customer not found", 404)
Ctrl --> API : 1.11.2: 404
API --> UI : 1.11.3: Lỗi
else 1.12: [Customer tồn tại]
Svc -> Svc : 1.12.1: _mapper.Map(request, customer)\n(chỉ cập nhật field != null)\ncustomer.UpdatedAt = UtcNow
Svc -> DB : 1.12.2: Customers.UpdateAsync(customer)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : OK
deactivate DB
Svc -> DB : 1.12.3: SaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.12.3.1: OK
deactivate DB

Svc -> Svc : 1.12.4: _mapper.Map<CustomerResponse>(customer)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.12.5: ApiResponse.Ok(data,\n"Customer updated successfully")
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.13: 200 OK
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.14: Response JSON
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.15: Cập nhật UI\n(invalidate cache)
UI --> User : 1.16: "Customer updated successfully"
deactivate UI

@enduml
